WEBVTT


00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.940
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:28.320
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:36.070
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:42.180
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:46.990
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:50.060
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:50.770 --> 00:00:55.720
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:56.760 --> 00:00:59.940
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:03.220
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:03.760 --> 00:01:08.890
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.920
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:16.280
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:22.360
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:26.020
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:29.350
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:33.790
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:35.040
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 38=

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:39.960
Chu Jiahe,

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:42.960
this isn't Ningzhou anymore.

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:45.640
You're not the lead anymore.

00:01:46.600 --> 00:01:47.720
Do you know how you got

00:01:47.720 --> 00:01:48.880
your Yang Pai Feng?

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.800
She had no time to perform it,

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:53.760
so it was handed to you.

00:01:54.560 --> 00:01:55.880
I heard it myself.

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:58.360
She told Troupe Leader Shan.

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:02.520
Or could you ever play the lead?

00:02:04.600 --> 00:02:06.040
I was such a fool.

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.520
I helped her so much,

00:02:09.040 --> 00:02:10.400
and she helped you.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:13.960
We grew up together.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.760
Why are you always above me?

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.280
Why do you get an apartment

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.560
while I'm stuck here?

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.680
In fact, you hate her more than I do.

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:29.120
If you'd met that writer that day,

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:32.600
would you tell him about this mess?

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:41.120
You will.

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:52.360
Chu Jiahe.

00:02:53.080 --> 00:02:54.520
I don't want your things.

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:55.440
Take them all away.

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:16.160
Come in.

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:20.840
Troupe Leader, can we talk?

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:23.280
Chu, perfect timing.

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:24.560
I was looking for you.

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:25.600
Come on, have a seat.

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:27.880
Sit.

00:03:29.320 --> 00:03:31.000
Then, you go first.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:32.400
All right.

00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:33.720
Here's the thing.

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:35.680
Shanghai Opera Festival

00:03:36.880 --> 00:03:38.800
likes Hu Xian Jie.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:41.400
But under their requirements,

00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:42.880
it must run

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:45.200
at least five shows before the festival.

00:03:45.720 --> 00:03:47.960
So, its rehearsal schedule

00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:49.720
may clash

00:03:49.720 --> 00:03:50.920
with Da Jiao Zan.

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:53.680
After thinking it over,

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:57.440
we'd like to put Da Jiao Zan on hold.

00:03:57.880 --> 00:03:58.800
That way,

00:03:58.800 --> 00:04:00.560
you'll have more time to rehearse.

00:04:01.600 --> 00:04:02.760
Why should I step aside?

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:04.880
We're not asking you to step aside.

00:04:04.880 --> 00:04:06.360
This is for your own good.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:09.440
If Hu Xian Jie and Da Jiao Zan

00:04:09.440 --> 00:04:11.320
start selling tickets together,

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:14.360
Da Jiao Zan may take the hit.

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:15.800
What do you think?

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:16.680
I'm not backing down.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.680
And I'm not scared.

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:26.280
Didn't you say you had more to tell me?

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:29.240
Not anymore.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.400
Another artist.

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:49.680
What?

00:04:50.086 --> 00:04:51.206
I need to ask you something.

00:04:52.280 --> 00:04:53.360
Spit it out.

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:57.880
How did Qin'e offend you?

00:04:58.679 --> 00:04:59.788
Why spread rumors about her?

00:04:59.880 --> 00:05:00.800
What rumors?

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.840
Keep acting. Go on, play dumb.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.280
You know what I mean.

00:05:04.760 --> 00:05:06.000
You started that rumor.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.760
I'm warning you.

00:05:07.760 --> 00:05:09.160
Don't pin this on me.

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:11.600
Still denying it?

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:14.600
I found who wrote that trashy article.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:15.760
He told me

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.160
the rumormonger was a classmate

00:05:17.160 --> 00:05:18.920
of Yi Qin'e from Ningzhou.

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:20.280
And it was a woman.

00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:22.320
Who else could it be?

00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:24.800
What are you doing?

00:05:25.440 --> 00:05:26.440
Are you going to hit me?

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:27.820
Come on. Hit me.

00:05:27.820 --> 00:05:28.660
Hit me right here.

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:29.880
Go on, hit me. Do it.

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:31.720
You think I won't dare?

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:33.760
What? What?

00:05:33.760 --> 00:05:35.400
What can you do? Come on.

00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:37.720
Are you crazy?

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:38.720
What are you doing?

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.360
I don't hit women, okay?

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:42.282
Shut up. What's wrong?

00:05:42.293 --> 00:05:43.300
- She's evil.
- Yi Qin'e,

00:05:43.300 --> 00:05:44.513
stop acting like a good person.

00:05:44.659 --> 00:05:45.859
Just because you're the lead

00:05:45.870 --> 00:05:46.962
and everyone fawns over you,

00:05:46.973 --> 00:05:48.600
it doesn't mean you can push me around.

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:50.840
I don't need your pity.

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:52.280
I'd rather quit Yang Pai Feng

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:53.560
than accept your charity.

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:54.800
Why are you talking nonsense?

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.080
I'm talking nonsense?

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:57.280
Ask your precious idol.

00:05:57.280 --> 00:05:58.720
Ask her what I made up.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:02.480
Who is Liao Yaohui
in Ningzhou's kitchen?

00:06:02.480 --> 00:06:03.600
What did he do to her?

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:05.800
Say it.

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:07.680
Say it!

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:14.440
Didn't you say I was talking nonsense?

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:15.800
Didn't you find out the truth?

00:06:16.120 --> 00:06:16.960
Say it.

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.560
What happened in that kitchen?

00:06:19.780 --> 00:06:20.640
Shut up!

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:21.880
Go check it out. I made it up?

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:23.082
- Huh?
- I'll tear your mouth.

00:06:23.093 --> 00:06:23.920
- Go on.
- Leave.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:24.880
- Come on.
- Leave.

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:25.720
Do it!

00:06:29.320 --> 00:06:30.880
Disgusting. Filthy.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:31.960
Ugh.

00:06:31.960 --> 00:06:33.640
Get out, or I'll beat you, you rotten...

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:35.480
Beat me, then.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:36.800
Beat me to death.

00:06:46.440 --> 00:06:47.910
Aren't you ashamed?

00:06:47.910 --> 00:06:49.560
Get out of here.

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:50.930
Have you no shame?

00:06:50.930 --> 00:06:51.800
What's it to you?

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:52.920
What are you staring at?

00:06:53.320 --> 00:06:54.720
Look all you want. Come on, look.

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:55.600
Move, move.

00:06:57.400 --> 00:06:58.240
Turn around.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:06:59.680
Okay.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:04.240
(Chu Jiahe was in turmoil.)

00:08:04.760 --> 00:08:07.240
(She was upset over Zhou Yuzhi,)

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:10.160
(bitter about being asked to yield,)

00:08:10.720 --> 00:08:13.800
(and angry at Liu Hongbing
for wronging her.)

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:15.640
(So, she spoke without thinking;)

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:17.160
(she was furious beyond control.)

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:21.040
(Chu Jiahe had always
outshone Yi Qin'e.)

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:23.160
(She came from a better family,)

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:24.720
(she sang and danced better,)

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:26.600
(and she was more admired.)

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:29.600
(But when)

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:31.240
(did all of that change?)

00:08:32.280 --> 00:08:33.120
(She didn't know.)

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:35.960
(That only made it harder to accept.)

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:39.040
(But what did Yi Qin'e do wrong?)

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:42.680
(It was a man who made a mistake,)

00:08:43.040 --> 00:08:45.720
(but why did two girls
have to suffer for it?)

00:09:35.440 --> 00:09:38.640
(Chang'an Youth Palace)
You have to know the meaning.

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.800
Through your singing,

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:43.280
let your feelings come through.

00:09:44.080 --> 00:09:45.960
That's how you move the audience.

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:48.680
Now, close your eyes.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:51.800
Try to feel the sunlight,

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:55.240
my voice,

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:59.400
and everything you can sense.

00:10:00.280 --> 00:10:01.600
Take a deep breath.

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:10.400
Just take it in slowly, okay?

00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:17.600
Sis.

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:21.120
How can you leave without saying hi?

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:24.200
I had errands and was passing by.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:25.400
So, I came for a visit.

00:10:25.880 --> 00:10:26.800
Nothing important.

00:10:28.400 --> 00:10:29.640
Look at you.

00:10:29.640 --> 00:10:31.720
Chairwoman, yet still teaching class.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:33.120
You sounded like a real pro.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.720
Be honest with me.

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.040
You just came to look around?

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:39.160
Of course.

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.480
Our Children's Palace

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:44.440
is starting an opera workshop.

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.680
Could a star like you give us tips?

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:49.200
What tips could I possibly give?

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:51.240
Let's talk about it later.

00:10:51.240 --> 00:10:52.720
Go on. I'll head out first.

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:55.440
I was about to come find you too.

00:10:56.120 --> 00:10:56.960
What's wrong?

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.080
Go check on Laidi.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:12.960
How did she come in?

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:22.960
Director Feng.

00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:24.400
Are you okay?

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:25.440
I'm fine.

00:11:27.059 --> 00:11:28.105
Shall we start rehearsing?

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:45.360
Come on, stop. Come on.

00:11:46.380 --> 00:11:47.240
Xue Guisheng,

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.440
does Qin'e have thorns on her?

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:51.520
Look at her.

00:11:53.720 --> 00:11:54.640
No, she doesn't.

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:57.520
Then why stand so far away?

00:11:58.040 --> 00:12:01.840
Next scene, you're torn apart.

00:12:02.180 --> 00:12:03.040
So, in this scene,

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.240
you two should be reaching

00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:06.640
an emotional breaking point.

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:09.040
Can you show some feeling?

00:12:09.840 --> 00:12:10.680
Again.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:18.720
Cut. Cut.

00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:20.960
Xue Guisheng,

00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:22.720
what's going on with you?

00:12:23.480 --> 00:12:24.520
Are you...

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:26.160
Is something on your mind?

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:28.320
Or are you scared of something?

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:30.520
He's scared of getting dragged in.

00:12:32.520 --> 00:12:33.600
He's so effeminate.

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:34.800
What's there to be scared of?

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:37.280
How ridiculous.

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:38.160
Wei Xiaohui,

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:40.040
are you done?

00:12:40.040 --> 00:12:41.120
What did I do?

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:42.920
Listen, I've had enough.

00:12:43.280 --> 00:12:44.440
How long has it been?

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:47.160
You keep whispering about me.

00:12:47.160 --> 00:12:49.120
Do you have any proof?

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:50.960
There are so many in the troupe.

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:52.320
Can't I even talk?

00:12:52.320 --> 00:12:54.320
Is every word I say about you?

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.280
Listen to me.

00:12:55.680 --> 00:12:57.120
There's nothing going on

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:59.720
between Yi Qin'e and me.

00:13:00.280 --> 00:13:01.820
When did I mention you and Yi Qin'e?

00:13:01.820 --> 00:13:02.710
Director,

00:13:02.710 --> 00:13:04.000
he's spreading rumors. See?

00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:05.520
Enough. Both of you, say less.

00:13:05.520 --> 00:13:07.760
You really play innocent well.

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:10.360
You're showing your true colors,

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:12.040
just like Bai after realgar wine.

00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:13.040
How so?

00:13:13.040 --> 00:13:14.520
You started the rumors.

00:13:14.520 --> 00:13:15.680
You nasty fraud!

00:13:17.780 --> 00:13:18.670
All right, all right.

00:13:18.670 --> 00:13:19.540
Break it up.

00:13:19.540 --> 00:13:20.380
All right, enough.

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:23.040
No, no. Let go. Stop.

00:13:23.040 --> 00:13:23.880
Let go. Let go.

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:27.680
Stop!

00:13:31.360 --> 00:13:32.600
This has nothing to do with you.

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.760
It's all my fault, okay?

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:44.920
Where are you going?

00:13:45.726 --> 00:13:46.852
You're not the one at fault.

00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:48.720
Who are you?

00:13:52.400 --> 00:13:53.240
I'm from Ningzhou.

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:56.360
When Yi Qin'e was a kitchen maid,

00:13:56.760 --> 00:13:58.320
I was with the County Troupe.

00:13:59.320 --> 00:14:00.760
There was never any trouble.

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:03.120
Now, you've twisted it into a scandal.

00:14:04.320 --> 00:14:05.320
All these years,

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:07.560
all those virtuous and righteous lines

00:14:07.560 --> 00:14:09.560
are for nothing.

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:16.080
Yi Qin'e is the victim.

00:14:16.480 --> 00:14:18.720
If you must blame someone,
blame the attacker

00:14:18.720 --> 00:14:20.440
and the ones spreading lies.

00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:22.840
Yet you've become one of them.

00:14:23.920 --> 00:14:24.760
Have you no shame?

00:14:25.320 --> 00:14:26.320
Have you no conscience?

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:31.960
And this is the provincial troupe?

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:34.360
I'm from the County Troupe,

00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:35.840
and I look down on you.

00:14:40.840 --> 00:14:41.680
Get your clothes.

00:14:42.200 --> 00:14:43.160
Come home with me.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:49.720
A bunch of spineless cowards.

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:51.480
Hey, why insult us?

00:14:52.040 --> 00:14:53.680
County Troupe people can do that?

00:14:54.280 --> 00:14:55.560
Ridiculous.

00:14:59.240 --> 00:15:00.280
Did you hear that?

00:15:00.920 --> 00:15:03.640
She's from the County Troupe,
but she's right.

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:06.840
A rehearsal room is sacred.

00:15:07.520 --> 00:15:08.720
Don't drag every messy thing

00:15:08.720 --> 00:15:09.960
into the rehearsal room.

00:15:10.800 --> 00:15:12.280
This is the provincial troupe.

00:15:14.680 --> 00:15:16.320
How did she get in?

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:21.200
No need to look.

00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:25.280
Aunt Hua,

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:26.880
why are you here?

00:15:28.433 --> 00:15:30.186
I should've been there
for you in Ningzhou.

00:15:31.080 --> 00:15:32.080
It's not too late now.

00:15:33.200 --> 00:15:34.040
Let's go home.

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:37.440
Don't stoop to her level.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:38.880
Why even mess with her?

00:15:38.880 --> 00:15:40.520
Just ignore her, and it'll be over.

00:15:40.520 --> 00:15:41.800
Does she look gentle to you?

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.720
She's stronger than I am.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:45.760
Look. Look.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:47.200
She scratched me up

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:49.120
and kicked me below the belt.

00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:51.920
Troupe Leader, I've been so wronged.

00:15:52.520 --> 00:15:54.640
Yi Qin'e and I have nothing going on.

00:15:54.640 --> 00:15:56.800
I'm as clean as a blank sheet.

00:15:56.800 --> 00:15:58.160
What do I have to fear?

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:03.920
I'll go get a purity test right now.

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:05.480
I'll bring the report back

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.920
and shove it in those jerks' faces.

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:07.820
Fine. Stick that report

00:16:07.820 --> 00:16:08.680
on your own face.

00:16:08.680 --> 00:16:10.000
You're embarrassing yourself.

00:16:10.520 --> 00:16:11.640
Go on, get back to work.

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:17.600
Just look at yourself.

00:16:18.880 --> 00:16:20.640
Yi Qin'e suffered

00:16:20.760 --> 00:16:22.480
just as much as you do.

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:23.320
Look at her.

00:16:23.680 --> 00:16:25.600
She knows that silence

00:16:25.600 --> 00:16:28.840
is the best answer to rumors.

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:30.080
Silence?

00:16:30.680 --> 00:16:33.240
She kicked me where it hurts!

00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:34.280
Just let her.

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:35.680
Just ignore her.

00:16:37.160 --> 00:16:38.360
I regret it so much.

00:16:38.920 --> 00:16:39.800
Regret what?

00:16:39.800 --> 00:16:41.840
That day, Wang Qinsheng acted up.

00:16:42.320 --> 00:16:44.760
Why did I have to help her?

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:45.760
Saving the damsel

00:16:45.760 --> 00:16:47.600
in distress is not for someone like me.

00:16:48.680 --> 00:16:51.320
I came all the way
from Tianshui to Chang'an.

00:16:52.280 --> 00:16:54.440
I wouldn't spend 30 cents on a bath.

00:16:54.800 --> 00:16:57.040
I couldn't spare one yuan for a book.

00:16:57.040 --> 00:16:58.840
Why was I trying to be a hero?

00:17:00.160 --> 00:17:01.880
You shouldn't be a Xiaosheng.

00:17:01.880 --> 00:17:03.320
You should be a Laodan.

00:17:05.440 --> 00:17:06.360
You think so too?

00:17:07.200 --> 00:17:08.680
When I first started out,

00:17:08.680 --> 00:17:10.720
my master did have me try Laodan.

00:17:10.720 --> 00:17:13.160
But look how my career turned out.

00:17:13.160 --> 00:17:14.960
I've let my master down.

00:17:16.040 --> 00:17:17.480
What a wimp.

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:18.920
Honestly.

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:22.200
All right, all right.

00:17:23.160 --> 00:17:24.760
On behalf of the troupe,

00:17:24.760 --> 00:17:26.200
I'll make this clear today.

00:17:26.200 --> 00:17:27.240
This matter

00:17:27.240 --> 00:17:28.480
will be investigated to the end.

00:17:29.920 --> 00:17:31.960
The troupe must clear my name.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:41.360
Aunt Hua didn't know about it.

00:17:42.320 --> 00:17:43.760
I upset her.

00:17:45.120 --> 00:17:47.120
Then you don't know Aunt Hua.

00:17:47.800 --> 00:17:49.240
She has a temper.

00:17:49.680 --> 00:17:51.640
She curses first and swings next.

00:17:51.960 --> 00:17:53.280
She just didn't know.

00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:54.440
If she had,

00:17:54.440 --> 00:17:56.240
she'd have long stood up for you.

00:17:56.240 --> 00:17:57.360
No way she'd wait till now.

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:03.040
Why are you here?

00:18:04.120 --> 00:18:05.240
I came to see you.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:09.000
A friend opened a factory in Fengyang

00:18:09.840 --> 00:18:11.480
and wanted seven days

00:18:11.480 --> 00:18:12.680
of your opera

00:18:13.080 --> 00:18:14.400
for the opening.

00:18:15.240 --> 00:18:16.080
What do you think?

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:24.720
I know what's on your mind.

00:18:27.040 --> 00:18:28.160
All these years,

00:18:28.760 --> 00:18:31.000
the awful people and messes I've faced

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:33.560
are beyond what you can imagine.

00:18:34.560 --> 00:18:36.080
I don't let them weigh on me.

00:18:36.080 --> 00:18:37.840
I just do what I need to do.

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:39.320
I keep my life full.

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:42.080
Over time, those things and people

00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:43.560
just stopped mattering to me.

00:18:43.800 --> 00:18:45.040
You won't care anymore.

00:18:46.640 --> 00:18:48.000
Isn't that just life?

00:18:49.120 --> 00:18:50.560
Keep your life full.

00:18:50.960 --> 00:18:51.800
Go sing opera.

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:54.840
Go.

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:57.040
Why wouldn't you?

00:18:57.040 --> 00:18:58.120
Just do what you should.

00:18:58.320 --> 00:18:59.319
Have your uncle go too.

00:18:59.330 --> 00:19:00.456
He'll play the drum for you.

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:04.840
Go.

00:19:44.440 --> 00:19:46.840
(Yi Qin'e does like Liu Hongbing.)

00:19:47.280 --> 00:19:49.280
(But something holds her back,)

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:51.280
(and that is Chef Liao.)

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:54.000
(She can't get past it.)

00:19:54.760 --> 00:19:56.000
(She even feels)

00:19:56.200 --> 00:19:58.000
(her feelings for Liu Hongbing)

00:19:58.320 --> 00:20:00.200
(have become a kind of debt.)

00:20:00.920 --> 00:20:01.760
(So,)

00:20:02.080 --> 00:20:03.320
(maybe leaving is for the best.)

00:20:04.080 --> 00:20:05.920
(She has no right to stay.)

00:20:09.140 --> 00:20:14.220
(Rehearsal Hall)

00:20:32.120 --> 00:20:32.960
Really?

00:20:32.960 --> 00:20:34.480
The troupe leader really decided?

00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:36.880
Those were his exact words.

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:37.800
This time,

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:39.840
even if he turns the troupe upside down,

00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:42.200
he'll find whoever spread the rumor.

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:43.960
Who do you think it is?

00:20:47.000 --> 00:20:47.840
Who do you think?

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:49.240
I didn't say a thing.

00:20:49.720 --> 00:20:51.160
Watch what you say lately.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:04.840
What's going on?

00:21:06.240 --> 00:21:07.680
Jiahe, I'm sorry.

00:21:08.240 --> 00:21:09.120
That day,

00:21:09.440 --> 00:21:10.980
I shouldn't have treated you that way.

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:13.040
About what I did,

00:21:13.480 --> 00:21:14.640
could you please

00:21:14.640 --> 00:21:16.080
not tell anyone else?

00:21:19.400 --> 00:21:21.280
Jiahe, I really regret it.

00:21:21.440 --> 00:21:23.200
The troupe leader is looking into it.

00:21:23.760 --> 00:21:25.280
If they find out that it was me,

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:28.960
I may get dismissed.

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:30.593
That's the troupe's business.

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:31.800
Jiahe,

00:21:31.800 --> 00:21:33.520
I'm not like you.

00:21:34.280 --> 00:21:35.840
I came from a small village.

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:38.440
My whole family is counting on me.

00:21:39.080 --> 00:21:41.000
If I lose this job,

00:21:41.960 --> 00:21:43.160
I'm finished.

00:21:45.200 --> 00:21:46.120
Jiahe,

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:48.320
I'm begging you.

00:21:50.680 --> 00:21:51.640
I need to rehearse.

00:22:13.040 --> 00:22:14.480
More chili.

00:22:15.840 --> 00:22:16.680
Here.

00:22:17.760 --> 00:22:18.600
Do you want soda?

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:19.800
No, I'm good.

00:22:23.680 --> 00:22:24.960
They've reached Fengyang.

00:22:25.640 --> 00:22:26.840
The opening night was packed.

00:22:27.053 --> 00:22:28.312
The boss added five more shows.

00:22:29.600 --> 00:22:30.840
That's really great news.

00:22:31.760 --> 00:22:33.920
About Sanyuan and Laidi this time,

00:22:33.920 --> 00:22:35.280
I really should thank you.

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:39.120
Did I hear that right?

00:22:39.600 --> 00:22:42.000
You actually said thank you?

00:22:43.080 --> 00:22:45.000
I can't handle that. Thanks.

00:22:45.800 --> 00:22:46.960
Then just enjoy your food.

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:50.200
Liangpi won't settle this.

00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:51.440
What else do you want?

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:56.200
Oh, the list is pretty long.

00:23:01.880 --> 00:23:02.720
Look at you.

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:05.560
Rou Jia Mo.

00:23:05.560 --> 00:23:06.680
Hele noodles.

00:23:07.560 --> 00:23:08.440
Jinggao.

00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:10.160
And that wasn't enough.

00:23:10.160 --> 00:23:12.360
You even wanted oil-splashed noodles.

00:23:12.840 --> 00:23:14.640
When was your appetite so huge?

00:23:15.560 --> 00:23:17.480
I've been saving it up for years.

00:23:17.480 --> 00:23:19.360
Isn't that our local specialty?

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:20.520
Carbs with more carbs.

00:23:27.520 --> 00:23:29.680
Is that thing you mentioned still on?

00:23:29.680 --> 00:23:30.520
What thing?

00:23:32.840 --> 00:23:34.520
Fine. Forget I said anything.

00:23:36.200 --> 00:23:37.040
I'm messing with you.

00:23:37.800 --> 00:23:39.200
I already set it up for you.

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:41.120
The moment I told them

00:23:41.120 --> 00:23:43.680
that you trained
the Little Queen of Qinqiang Opera,

00:23:43.680 --> 00:23:45.800
they nodded like pecking chickens.

00:23:48.040 --> 00:23:50.280
I was so worried before coming here.

00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:52.040
I kept thinking how to tell you.

00:23:52.040 --> 00:23:53.280
I was afraid you'd say no.

00:23:55.760 --> 00:23:56.840
After all these years,

00:23:57.840 --> 00:23:59.800
I've had dinner

00:24:00.400 --> 00:24:01.559
and spent every night alone.

00:24:02.680 --> 00:24:04.800
I really wanted someone to talk to.

00:24:05.327 --> 00:24:06.813
If you don't mind, stay here tonight.

00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:08.520
That's exactly what I planned.

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:10.440
Think about us back then.

00:24:10.440 --> 00:24:11.419
I don't even know

00:24:11.430 --> 00:24:12.760
why we fought over those things.

00:24:12.760 --> 00:24:13.600
Was it worth it?

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:15.760
Worth what?

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.320
All the stuff we did back then

00:24:19.560 --> 00:24:21.600
honestly makes me laugh now.

00:24:23.400 --> 00:24:24.560
But it was fun, wasn't it?

00:24:25.440 --> 00:24:26.400
At least back then,

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:28.560
you had a rival to spar with.

00:24:29.320 --> 00:24:31.200
Now, there's no competition.

00:24:31.900 --> 00:24:32.760
You know what?

00:24:32.760 --> 00:24:33.920
I often dream about our days

00:24:33.920 --> 00:24:35.600
at the Ningzhou County Troupe.

00:24:37.800 --> 00:24:39.280
I still dream

00:24:41.000 --> 00:24:42.440
about singing opera onstage.

00:24:43.280 --> 00:24:44.320
I'm the lead.

00:24:44.760 --> 00:24:46.000
I'm Li Tiemei.

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:47.080
And you are Grandma Li.

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:49.280
But whenever I call you Grandma,

00:24:49.280 --> 00:24:50.160
you never answer me.

00:24:51.106 --> 00:24:52.146
Because you don't mean it.

00:24:52.720 --> 00:24:54.080
If you meant it even a little

00:24:54.080 --> 00:24:55.080
and called out louder,

00:24:55.080 --> 00:24:56.480
I'd hear it even in my dreams

00:24:56.480 --> 00:24:58.080
and answer you loud and clear.

00:24:59.640 --> 00:25:01.800
♪Grandma, listen to me♪

00:25:01.800 --> 00:25:03.080
Just eat already.

00:25:06.080 --> 00:25:08.720
You're Ningzhou's Liangpi Queen.

00:25:08.720 --> 00:25:09.920
Queen? That's too much.

00:25:10.520 --> 00:25:11.640
Maybe Xi Shi.

00:25:28.160 --> 00:25:33.640
Bravo!

00:25:44.720 --> 00:25:46.040
Great!

00:25:46.400 --> 00:25:47.920
Bravo!

00:25:47.920 --> 00:25:48.760
Great!

00:25:55.880 --> 00:25:56.720
Everyone,

00:25:58.600 --> 00:26:00.880
for the lead in the troupe,

00:26:02.120 --> 00:26:04.840
strange things often happen.

00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:06.840
So, this recent incident

00:26:06.840 --> 00:26:07.960
is not an isolated case.

00:26:08.400 --> 00:26:09.920
We need to resolve this.

00:26:10.560 --> 00:26:11.400
First,

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:15.240
we must clear Yi Qin'e's name.

00:26:15.720 --> 00:26:16.560
Second,

00:26:16.680 --> 00:26:19.960
we must stop this from happening again.

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:22.560
You can interpret this

00:26:22.560 --> 00:26:24.480
as me making an example out of someone.

00:26:25.720 --> 00:26:28.520
But who's the example,
and who's the audience?

00:26:28.520 --> 00:26:30.160
Think carefully about that.

00:26:33.920 --> 00:26:34.920
Here and now,

00:26:34.920 --> 00:26:37.280
we're giving the instigator
another chance

00:26:38.560 --> 00:26:40.160
to step forward and confess.

00:26:40.160 --> 00:26:41.080
Troupe Leader,

00:26:41.560 --> 00:26:42.720
what chance do they deserve?

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:44.680
Just take them to the station.

00:26:44.680 --> 00:26:45.840
Shut your mouth.

00:26:51.080 --> 00:26:52.560
No one admits, huh?

00:26:52.860 --> 00:26:53.750
Fine.

00:26:53.750 --> 00:26:55.040
Then I'll hand this matter

00:26:55.040 --> 00:26:56.320
to the Wenyi Road Police Station.

00:26:56.320 --> 00:26:57.240
Let pros

00:26:57.240 --> 00:26:59.690
like Chief Qiao handle it.

00:26:59.780 --> 00:27:00.640
Come on, confess!

00:27:00.640 --> 00:27:01.480
It was me.

00:27:09.840 --> 00:27:11.800
You've suspected me all along, right?

00:27:13.360 --> 00:27:14.560
Well, you were right.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:16.040
I did it.

00:27:17.200 --> 00:27:18.280
Chu Jiahe,

00:27:18.280 --> 00:27:19.680
why did you do this?

00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:21.040
Envy.

00:27:21.480 --> 00:27:22.320
Jealousy.

00:27:22.560 --> 00:27:23.400
Resentment.

00:27:23.560 --> 00:27:24.400
Why?

00:27:24.880 --> 00:27:25.720
Is that not allowed?

00:27:28.080 --> 00:27:30.240
Since I got here from Ningzhou,

00:27:30.240 --> 00:27:33.200
how many days has it been?

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:34.520
I don't even know.

00:27:36.120 --> 00:27:37.160
All I know is

00:27:38.280 --> 00:27:39.960
that I've never played the lead.

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:43.240
It's always endless bit parts

00:27:43.880 --> 00:27:45.200
and endless maid roles.

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:48.240
I think many of you here

00:27:48.240 --> 00:27:50.640
feel the same.

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:53.120
We've trained since we were kids.

00:27:53.120 --> 00:27:54.720
Who hasn't been pushed to the limit?

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.600
All those tears and sweat

00:27:57.080 --> 00:27:59.160
are to become the lead.

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:02.480
I think I've worked so hard.

00:28:03.600 --> 00:28:05.360
But I still can't become the lead.

00:28:07.280 --> 00:28:09.040
So, I keep asking myself:

00:28:10.200 --> 00:28:11.840
What am I still missing?

00:28:16.120 --> 00:28:17.520
So, have you figured it out?

00:28:17.960 --> 00:28:18.800
What are you missing?

00:28:19.160 --> 00:28:20.000
No.

00:28:20.713 --> 00:28:21.873
I stopped thinking about it.

00:28:24.680 --> 00:28:26.640
I wronged Comrade Yi Qin'e.

00:28:27.440 --> 00:28:29.320
I made the whole thing up

00:28:30.080 --> 00:28:31.880
and told that writer.

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:33.520
I made a mistake.

00:28:34.160 --> 00:28:35.960
I'll take full responsibility.

00:28:38.200 --> 00:28:39.480
Please remove me from the troupe.

00:28:43.520 --> 00:28:44.880
Don't rush into this.

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:46.080
Your punishment

00:28:46.080 --> 00:28:47.480
is up to the troupe.

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:49.160
For now, you just need

00:28:49.320 --> 00:28:50.920
to reflect on it seriously.

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:52.360
Reflect on what?

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:55.160
That I'm not good enough?

00:28:55.160 --> 00:28:56.360
Or that fate isn't on my side?

00:28:56.680 --> 00:28:57.640
Don't talk like that.

00:28:58.000 --> 00:28:59.000
The troupe

00:28:59.000 --> 00:29:01.160
chooses the lead based

00:29:01.160 --> 00:29:02.080
on various factors.

00:29:02.080 --> 00:29:03.160
I don't need that.

00:29:05.560 --> 00:29:07.960
All the rumors started because of me.

00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:09.520
Once I leave,

00:29:10.040 --> 00:29:11.840
everything should calm down.

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:16.680
Please take this as a warning

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:19.160
and stop giving Yi Qin'e a hard time.

00:29:22.400 --> 00:29:23.240
Well, this...

00:29:30.320 --> 00:29:31.160
Quiet, quiet.

00:29:32.440 --> 00:29:34.600
About Chu Jiahe's statement today,

00:29:34.920 --> 00:29:36.880
you may discuss it among yourselves.

00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:38.080
But let me make this clear:

00:29:38.080 --> 00:29:39.640
If anyone keeps talking nonsense

00:29:39.640 --> 00:29:41.520
or spreading rumors,

00:29:41.520 --> 00:29:43.520
I'll deal with them, and I mean it.

00:29:43.520 --> 00:29:44.360
Is that clear?

00:29:44.500 --> 00:29:45.360
Yes.

00:29:45.360 --> 00:29:46.200
Dismissed.

00:29:49.760 --> 00:29:51.320
Was a role really worth all that?

00:29:52.240 --> 00:29:54.000
She has too much free time.

00:29:56.960 --> 00:29:57.800
So stubborn.

00:30:16.040 --> 00:30:18.760
This looks familiar, doesn't it?

00:30:22.480 --> 00:30:23.320
That was amazing.

00:30:23.480 --> 00:30:24.320
Keep it up.

00:30:24.680 --> 00:30:25.520
That's great.

00:30:29.680 --> 00:30:31.400
Yi Qin'e, I finally meet you.

00:30:34.320 --> 00:30:35.800
What's on your mind?

00:30:36.480 --> 00:30:37.320
Nothing.

00:30:39.060 --> 00:30:39.920
In this whole trip,

00:30:39.920 --> 00:30:42.400
you barely said a word to me.

00:30:42.400 --> 00:30:43.520
What is there to say?

00:30:44.320 --> 00:30:45.400
This kid...

00:30:45.400 --> 00:30:46.960
You just don't talk much.

00:30:48.160 --> 00:30:49.680
If something's weighing on you,

00:30:49.680 --> 00:30:50.880
you'll feel better saying it.

00:30:51.720 --> 00:30:53.720
Bottling it up only hurts more.

00:30:54.520 --> 00:30:56.520
If I say it, more people will know.

00:30:56.520 --> 00:30:58.760
That only makes the pain last longer.

00:31:01.880 --> 00:31:03.120
Don't worry, Uncle.

00:31:03.120 --> 00:31:04.480
Once I sing opera, I'll be fine.

00:31:07.480 --> 00:31:08.400
To be honest,

00:31:09.120 --> 00:31:10.360
I've spent my life

00:31:10.360 --> 00:31:11.520
around the stage,

00:31:12.680 --> 00:31:13.800
and I've never seen

00:31:13.800 --> 00:31:15.520
a star performer as loved as you.

00:31:16.600 --> 00:31:19.640
So, with what you're facing now,

00:31:19.640 --> 00:31:20.760
I can't use my experience

00:31:21.240 --> 00:31:22.960
to fix it for you.

00:31:30.080 --> 00:31:31.280
It'll all pass, right?

00:31:33.240 --> 00:31:34.600
No matter how sad it gets,

00:31:35.200 --> 00:31:36.040
or how much it hurts.

00:31:38.400 --> 00:31:39.240
Right.

00:31:39.600 --> 00:31:40.680
That's why people

00:31:40.680 --> 00:31:42.040
have to live in the present.

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:44.840
Right?

00:31:48.560 --> 00:31:50.000
Some things

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:51.520
only seem precious once they're gone.

00:31:53.120 --> 00:31:54.640
I should've cherished it sooner.

00:31:56.840 --> 00:31:58.080
You mean Liu Hongbing?

00:32:00.480 --> 00:32:01.360
No.

00:32:01.640 --> 00:32:03.280
You have feelings for him, huh?

00:32:03.600 --> 00:32:05.000
What are you saying, Uncle?

00:32:06.920 --> 00:32:07.960
Relax. Relax.

00:32:08.440 --> 00:32:10.160
If it's yours, he won't get away.

00:32:10.600 --> 00:32:12.393
If you can't get through this,

00:32:12.404 --> 00:32:13.524
there's no need to feel bad.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:14.840
Right?

00:32:16.480 --> 00:32:17.400
Don't overthink it.

00:32:23.420 --> 00:32:24.500
(Qinqiang Opera Show)

00:32:55.380 --> 00:32:56.315
(Everything shall pass)

00:32:56.326 --> 00:32:57.420
(and become a fond memory.)

00:32:57.420 --> 00:32:58.620
(Best wishes for Hu Xian Jie.)

00:32:58.620 --> 00:33:00.300
(Mi Lan)

00:33:23.720 --> 00:33:26.080
Why clean this old clunker?

00:33:26.960 --> 00:33:29.560
You're officially at Children's Palace,

00:33:29.560 --> 00:33:31.360
teaching the children's opera class.

00:33:31.800 --> 00:33:32.680
You won't need it.

00:33:32.680 --> 00:33:33.800
Why not let it go?

00:33:34.800 --> 00:33:36.680
It's fed me all these years.

00:33:37.240 --> 00:33:38.400
I've grown attached to it.

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:40.560
Fine. I'll carry on your legacy.

00:33:41.800 --> 00:33:42.640
Leave it to me.

00:33:43.520 --> 00:33:45.440
The private booking is coming up.

00:33:45.440 --> 00:33:46.860
You'll be busier than I am soon.

00:33:48.520 --> 00:33:49.400
I'll push it back

00:33:50.360 --> 00:33:51.680
and give it a little upgrade.

00:33:52.200 --> 00:33:55.120
It'll come in handy for us later.

00:33:57.560 --> 00:33:59.560
We really owe Mi Lan this time.

00:34:00.080 --> 00:34:01.400
Not just you.

00:34:01.400 --> 00:34:03.280
Qin'e and I both owe her.

00:34:03.760 --> 00:34:05.360
Let's treat her to dinner sometime.

00:34:06.440 --> 00:34:07.280
She left.

00:34:08.280 --> 00:34:09.120
Left?

00:34:10.240 --> 00:34:11.640
Where to? Why so sudden?

00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:13.360
She said something came up.

00:34:13.360 --> 00:34:15.080
She left in a rush yesterday.

00:34:15.840 --> 00:34:17.000
I went to see her off.

00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:18.400
Before she left, she said something

00:34:18.800 --> 00:34:20.200
that really stuck with me.

00:34:21.760 --> 00:34:22.600
She said

00:34:23.840 --> 00:34:24.840
that in this world,

00:34:24.840 --> 00:34:28.040
no one can really save anyone else.

00:34:28.680 --> 00:34:30.520
She just went along with the flow.

00:34:31.000 --> 00:34:32.880
These things were meant to happen.

00:34:34.040 --> 00:34:35.840
No one can change a thing.

00:34:36.880 --> 00:34:38.520
So, that really was Mi Lan.

00:34:39.360 --> 00:34:40.200
What is it?

00:34:41.160 --> 00:34:42.880
It just feels unreal.

00:34:43.840 --> 00:34:45.120
She drifted in so lightly,

00:34:45.600 --> 00:34:46.600
like some kind

00:34:47.480 --> 00:34:48.560
of fox spirit.

00:34:49.800 --> 00:34:51.040
She came to enlighten us.

00:34:52.520 --> 00:34:54.960
If she were, it'd be fate.

00:34:55.360 --> 00:34:57.880
Qin'e's Hu Xian Jie will blow up.

00:34:59.200 --> 00:35:00.040
Exactly.

00:35:01.240 --> 00:35:02.080
As it should be.

00:35:03.920 --> 00:35:04.760
A hit.

00:35:17.640 --> 00:35:18.760
When did you get back?

00:35:18.760 --> 00:35:19.600
Mom.

00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:25.440
Why are you sitting here?

00:35:26.120 --> 00:35:26.960
I'm tired.

00:35:30.960 --> 00:35:32.400
Hongbing, eat more.

00:35:32.400 --> 00:35:33.600
You've lost weight.

00:35:37.120 --> 00:35:39.160
Are they nice at the local office?

00:35:41.040 --> 00:35:41.880
They're great.

00:35:42.480 --> 00:35:43.960
They give me the easy work

00:35:43.960 --> 00:35:45.400
for my dad's sake.

00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:46.800
Why did you come back?

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:50.800
I missed you and Mom,

00:35:50.800 --> 00:35:51.640
so I came to see you.

00:36:02.320 --> 00:36:03.160
Eat up, eat up.

00:36:08.800 --> 00:36:09.720
Oh, Mom.

00:36:10.640 --> 00:36:11.840
Where's our household register?

00:36:12.160 --> 00:36:13.080
Why?

00:36:13.080 --> 00:36:15.000
We need temporary residence permits.

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:16.600
They need it for registration.

00:36:17.160 --> 00:36:18.153
I'll get it after dinner.

00:36:18.800 --> 00:36:19.640
Okay.

00:36:35.260 --> 00:36:36.150
Yi Qin'e.

00:36:36.150 --> 00:36:37.200
Hurry, answer the phone.

00:36:37.200 --> 00:36:39.040
Beishan long-distance. Urgent. Hurry.

00:36:40.800 --> 00:36:41.640
Hello?

00:36:41.840 --> 00:36:43.066
Hongbing jumped off a building.

00:36:43.240 --> 00:36:44.080
Get over here, now.

00:36:44.440 --> 00:36:45.640
What happened to Liu Hongbing?

00:36:46.000 --> 00:36:47.640
He jumped off a building because of you.

00:36:47.640 --> 00:36:48.480
Hurry up.

00:36:48.680 --> 00:36:49.640
Where is he?

00:36:50.160 --> 00:36:51.240
Beishan Hospital.

00:36:51.480 --> 00:36:52.320
Hurry up.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:56.720
What happened?

00:37:12.160 --> 00:37:13.000
Excuse me.

00:37:13.280 --> 00:37:14.520
Where is Liu Hongbing?

00:37:14.531 --> 00:37:15.421
With so many patients,

00:37:15.432 --> 00:37:16.640
how can I remember every name?

00:37:16.651 --> 00:37:18.093
The one who jumped off the building.

00:37:18.640 --> 00:37:19.480
That one?

00:37:19.720 --> 00:37:21.200
Second floor, the room at the end.

00:37:21.200 --> 00:37:22.040
Thank you. Thank you.

00:37:22.400 --> 00:37:23.240
Sorry.

00:37:44.120 --> 00:37:45.400
How did you end up like this?

00:37:48.880 --> 00:37:50.280
You can't die.

00:37:50.720 --> 00:37:52.720
If you die, how can I face you?

00:37:54.800 --> 00:37:56.160
You can't die.

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:57.040
Who is she?

00:37:57.960 --> 00:37:58.800
Who is she?

00:37:59.280 --> 00:38:00.120
Who are you?

00:38:00.840 --> 00:38:02.200
I'm looking for Liu Hongbing.

00:38:03.880 --> 00:38:05.200
I'm here.

00:38:06.080 --> 00:38:07.880
You scared me. Wrong person.

00:38:10.080 --> 00:38:11.200
I'm sorry.

00:38:11.880 --> 00:38:13.160
I mistook him for someone else.

00:38:13.160 --> 00:38:14.000
Don't move.

00:38:15.440 --> 00:38:16.880
- You scared me sick.
- Don't.

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:18.040
Please, don't.

00:38:18.040 --> 00:38:19.080
Is it serious?

00:38:21.360 --> 00:38:22.720
Why did you jump off a building?

00:38:23.280 --> 00:38:24.720
Who jumped off a building?

00:38:25.060 --> 00:38:25.950
Sit down.

00:38:25.950 --> 00:38:26.920
I'll explain it slowly.

00:38:27.360 --> 00:38:28.200
Come on.

00:38:29.760 --> 00:38:31.080
I'm fine. Don't worry.

00:38:31.760 --> 00:38:33.473
I went home to get
the household register.

00:38:33.720 --> 00:38:35.880
But my old man was sharp.

00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:37.226
He caught me once I went upstairs.

00:38:38.120 --> 00:38:39.760
Then he locked me in my room.

00:38:40.080 --> 00:38:41.960
I was afraid you'd get worried,

00:38:41.960 --> 00:38:43.640
not knowing where I'd gone.

00:38:43.640 --> 00:38:44.880
So, I tried to climb down,

00:38:45.600 --> 00:38:47.600
but I fell.

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:50.720
Why take the household register?

00:38:50.720 --> 00:38:52.040
To register our marriage.

00:38:53.720 --> 00:38:55.640
I wanted to shut those people up.

00:38:56.240 --> 00:38:57.400
Once we're registered,

00:38:57.400 --> 00:38:58.640
we'll be legit.

00:38:58.880 --> 00:39:01.120
Let's see who still dares to gossip.

00:39:15.080 --> 00:39:16.080
You called her here?

00:39:17.320 --> 00:39:18.560
I just feel bad for Hongbing.

00:39:18.560 --> 00:39:19.760
Why meddle?

00:39:27.200 --> 00:39:28.120
That's great.

00:39:29.680 --> 00:39:30.520
This is

00:39:31.200 --> 00:39:32.920
your first time crying for me.

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:36.320
What's so good about crying?

00:39:37.320 --> 00:39:39.080
It means you care about me.

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:41.840
I'm so happy. So happy.

00:39:42.760 --> 00:39:44.600
I was worried sick, and you're happy?

00:39:45.120 --> 00:39:46.000
Don't hit me. Don't.

00:39:46.000 --> 00:39:48.040
It really hurts. It hurts.

00:39:54.120 --> 00:39:55.280
Lie down, now.

00:40:58.080 --> 00:40:58.920
Qin'e.

00:40:59.680 --> 00:41:00.960
Do you need the bathroom?

00:41:01.600 --> 00:41:02.440
No, no.

00:41:02.800 --> 00:41:04.440
You've been like this all night.

00:41:04.440 --> 00:41:05.280
You must be tired.

00:41:06.080 --> 00:41:07.440
I'll sit over there for a while.

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:08.360
You lie up here.

00:41:09.360 --> 00:41:10.200
No, no, it's okay.

00:41:11.320 --> 00:41:12.160
You're the patient.

00:41:12.160 --> 00:41:13.680
How can I take your bed?

00:41:14.280 --> 00:41:15.480
I've been lying down all night.

00:41:15.480 --> 00:41:16.840
My muscles are getting sore.

00:41:17.800 --> 00:41:19.400
I'll sit over there for a bit.

00:41:19.400 --> 00:41:21.920
- Lie down here.
- No, stop messing around.

00:41:21.920 --> 00:41:23.160
Or I'll get mad.

00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:24.760
Lie down. Now.

00:41:25.440 --> 00:41:26.280
Are you lying down?

00:41:26.640 --> 00:41:27.480
What are you doing?

00:41:28.760 --> 00:41:29.600
If you don't come up,

00:41:30.040 --> 00:41:31.400
I'll turn that crack into a break.

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:34.800
Seriously, stop it.

00:41:34.920 --> 00:41:36.360
Everyone else is asleep.

00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:38.720
If you don't come up,

00:41:38.720 --> 00:41:40.640
no one's getting any sleep.

00:41:47.840 --> 00:41:48.680
Happy now?

00:41:49.087 --> 00:41:50.600
- That's more like it.
- Go to sleep.

00:41:51.720 --> 00:41:52.693
I'll make room for you.

00:41:57.080 --> 00:41:57.920
See?

00:41:58.280 --> 00:41:59.360
Isn't this nice?

00:42:07.600 --> 00:42:08.440
Qin'e,

00:42:11.160 --> 00:42:13.120
if we could always be like this,

00:42:14.960 --> 00:42:15.880
that would be better.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:18.400
Even dying would be worth it.

00:42:20.200 --> 00:42:22.200
Can you not say such unlucky things?

00:42:23.440 --> 00:42:24.280
Right, you're right.

00:42:42.280 --> 00:42:43.120
Qin'e,

00:42:45.280 --> 00:42:47.120
no matter what happened before,

00:42:48.680 --> 00:42:49.520
I don't care.

00:42:52.240 --> 00:42:53.080
I promise.

00:42:54.880 --> 00:42:56.320
I'll never make you cry again.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.360 --> 00:43:12.560
Timing, place, and people
all have to line up

00:43:12.560 --> 00:43:14.080
to make one the lead.

00:43:14.080 --> 00:43:15.360
Now Qin'e is mine to care.

00:43:15.590 --> 00:43:16.640
(A match made in heaven)
Just rest assured!

00:43:16.640 --> 00:43:17.800
Good!

00:43:18.160 --> 00:43:19.960
She has her own ideas.

00:43:20.080 --> 00:43:21.360
At the height of her glory,

00:43:21.360 --> 00:43:22.520
she stepped away.

00:43:22.520 --> 00:43:25.160
Beishan's district lines have changed.

00:43:25.160 --> 00:43:27.640
And our administrative office faces cuts.

00:43:28.080 --> 00:43:29.880
- But stay alert.
- Who is that?

00:43:29.880 --> 00:43:32.160
- Don't fall into a trap that costs you all.
- Mi Lan?

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

00:45:52.020 --> 00:46:01.050
♪Already shouted across Qinchuan Plain♪